Text: Hi, guys :) I have a question / potential favor to ask if your schedules allow!

Kim’s rehearsal dinner is Thursday, Feb 16th - I plan to bring the kids to the actual rehearsal to give them a lay of the land. 

James doesn’t love crowds and can get easily overwhelmed, so I’m trying to mitigate things for him as Friday will no doubt be a lot ❤️
Maryn could hang, but the rehearsal itself doesn’t even start until 7 so it could be a late night

So my request is - if you are not working/are available Thursday evening, would either of you/both of you be open to spending time with the kids at the hotel that evening so they don’t have to come to the dinner?
You can order room service/eat at the hotel, watch a movie, okay games, whatever :)
Hi Kel! Sorry for late text just getting home from work!! Let me chat with Steve and keep you posted tomorrow! Thanks for your patience! ☺️
Hi Kel!! I’m not working on the 16th wahoooo so I/we will be there!!!! ☺️☺️☺️
